ai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834720/extras/92cb1124ebaaaae196be3752458fb07d.webp?t=1737839660\" width=46 height=36 /></span>     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834720/extras/40d7b458db55b2434ddaeabaacb1af4e.webp?t=1737839660\" width=64 height=48 /></span>    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834720/extras/b0ad61fadcfd4ca39cefac7197b75fdc.webp?t=1737839660\" width=64 height=48 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834720/extras/71748e32c11a05f9eb64c18e0cc9b504.webp?t=1737839660\" width=42 height=34 /></span>    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834720/extras/ea0318439d55fd91c18c8db0a20d4378.avif?t=1737839660\" width=74 height=64 /></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > A saga for the whole family.</h2></strong><br><br>Blossom la Jirafa collects the two games launched in one with the following characteristics<br><br>* Travel together with blossom through the urban landscapes of the city until her way home avoiding the enemies who will try to grab her<br><br>* Travel through the levels, in the city, subway and ship, find fruits to recover your lives.<br><br>* Play a runner with a retro aesthetic in the first Blossom installment and a horizontal action Platformer in its sequel.<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834720/extras/3b66b35e967c7dfce02efde3f7197249.avif?t=1737839660\" width=552 height=552 /></span>",
